(2, 2, 'About us', 'We believe that the past is the best indicator of the future and through truly understanding the past we can all make better decisions about the future. The problem is that as the world speeds up the time and desire to look backwards decreases and the lessons that history offers us are being lost, ignored or missed. And we want to change that by redefining everyone’s relationship with history through creating exciting and immersive experiences that bring the past to life. \r\n<br></br>\r\nHidden History offers a new way for you to engage with the past by turning the streets your walk along into the museum you never knew existed. The Hidden History app will guide you to points of interest and with the help of technology and a little bit of creativity, we will bring each location to life. You will leave each location with enough information from all sides of the event to enable you to draw your own conclusions about what it tells you about our world today and what it could mean about tomorrow.\r\n<br></br>\r\nHidden History is ideal for anyone who enjoys finding hidden ‘secrets’, finding new ideas and likes to explore a city’s hidden past freely and independently. \r\n<br></br>\r\nWe hope you enjoy Hidden History. \r\n\r\n');
