(1, 'Kieran', 'An enthuastic amateur historian with a passion for the past and a determination to play a small part in creating a better future. Leads the formation of the HH team and delivery of the project.', '', 'hidden1history', '', '', 'KieranPicture.jpg', 'Founder', 1),
(3, 'Elisha', 'With a BA (Hons) in History, Elisha loves a range of social and cultural histories and will be focusing on finding and exploring museums, exhibitions and festivals across the UK. \r\nIf you’re ever stuck for ideas for a historical day out, then Elisha will be able to help! Please let us know if there are any museums, exhibitions or festivals you think we should cover here at HH.', '', 'Elisha_Coates', '', '', 'Elisha.jpg', 'Head of Museums, Exhibtions &amp; Festivals ', 2),
(4, 'Anna ', 'BA in History and currently studying for an MA in Public History. Particularly passionate about medical and disease history; anything with bleeding/screaming/dying! Researches various historical figures and sites for the HH app and website. ', '', 'SuttyAnnacliffe', '', '', 'Anna.jpg', 'Historical Research &amp; Writter', 3),
(6, 'Elaine ', 'Graduated from the University of Sheffield in 2014 with a BA in History and is currently studying for an MA in Public History at the University of York where she enjoys exploring how history is represented within the media.', '', 'Elaine2995', '', '', 'Elaine.jpg', 'Historical Researcher &amp; Writer', 5),
(7, 'Ben', 'Ben is a journalist and historian who enjoys uncovering new things, which he had no idea happened or existed. He is a big motorsports and gaming fan who loves to travel. Ben will be focusing on the military and social history.', '', 'BDGrindle', '', '', 'Ben.jpg', 'Historical Researcher &amp; Writer', 6),
(8, 'Emma', 'Emma is a primary school teacher with a passion for history and disseminating stories from our past that give a voice to those that have been marginalized or hidden from traditional historical narratives. Emma is going to be leading on the Roman Empire and its impact then and legacy it left behind.', '', 'MrsSlinger', '', '', 'Emma.jpg', 'Historical Researcher &amp; Writer', 7),
(10, 'Jenny ', 'With a BA in Italian and History of Art and an MA in Egyptian Archaeology, Jenny has acquired a varied historical knowledge and interest. On a local scale, she is interested in Victorian London, with a particular fondness for the Pre-Raphaelites. Globally, her interests include Renaissance Italian painting and philosophy, Ancient Egypt religion, language, and art, and Korean art history, language, and popular culture.', '', 'jenniferanne89', '', '', 'Jenny.jpg', 'Historical Researcher &amp; Writer', 9),
(11, 'Sophie ', 'A PhD student at University of York working with the National Railway Museum researching commemorative cultures of the British railway industry. Sophie is A lover of sharing historical knowledge with the public. ', '', 'sophievohra', '', '', 'Sophie.jpg', 'Historical Researcher &amp; Writer', 10),
(12, 'Laura ', 'Laura is nearing the end of a PhD in the history of medicine is looking forward to expanding her interests again and uncovering some hidden stories from the past! Laura will be leading on the Victorians for Hidden History. ', '', 'Laur_Mainwaring', '', '', 'laura6.jpg', 'Historical Researcher &amp; Writer', 11),
(13, 'Michael CXT', 'Michael CXT is a visual graphics artist with a university degree in Environmental Management and Toxicology. His passion for the environment and its history over the years has had him express his views through visual art.\r\n\r\nAs the Head of Design &amp; Capability development, Michael was the brainchild behind the HH banner concept and his approach and talent is going to be instrumental in re-engaging the world with history.\r\n', '', 'Michael_cxt', '', '', 'Michael-CXT.jpg', 'Graphic Artist', 0),
(16, 'Shane', 'Shane is a military history aficionado whose interest stretches from the earliest recorded warfare between Mesopotamian city-states right through to recent conflicts in the Middle East. His passion on the subject has seen him travel the world visiting battlefields and related sites and he will be taking the lead on the military side of things for Hidden History.', '', 'WarGen39_45', '', '', 'shane.jpg', '', 12);
